s/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0b462e34c620ca407681ce9cf8f947ee09a8c4","tid":2402053,"uid":208227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"收購物業之後總資產升咗 到時保持到50%樓下咪無問題 唔係咁玩嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n同埋借俾關連公司收幾多租好似要過證監同受托人，唔係你話交一蚊租就一蚊租<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab7d5740715fcee54b39e8a7422c8a3138ee5ef","tid":2402053,"uid":86449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"諗起隻1503<br />\n上完巿係咁跌<br />\n賺息蝕價都無用<br />\n<br />\n不過而家物流資產估值都高左好多<br />\n有d cap 水 上巿 feel<br />\n如果資產估值仲有得升就另作別論<br />\n<br />\n當年778 上巿都係得幾個商場，係咁做垃圾桶先谷到而家咁大<br />\n唔知呢隻係唔係都想咁玩"},{"pid":"cc68b3af192bbfaef2018a0b32bd305ccb2e898b","tid":2402053,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"772e3f1242f1df37d79b7e68b3053a80436f16ca","tid":2402053,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"樓主見你講舊經濟多 會唔會分析下tech股？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"Price Dream ratio 嘅tech 唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他傳統tech 我持有:<br />\nadbe msft goog V<br />\n仲有啲唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead2fd40025361d35500714363cd8b77e29d2426","tid":2402053,"uid":63157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個時勢都4.2%息真係抵玩<br />\n2022年續期仲可以再加息tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525f0a9d23210c5ab7e7dad9bf48ff84dcad96b3","tid":2402053,"uid":246729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"be0b462e34c620ca407681ce9cf8f947ee09a8c4","tid":2402053,"uid":208227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"收購物業之後總資產升咗 到時保持到50%樓下咪無問題 唔係咁玩嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n同埋借俾關連公司收幾多租好似要過證監同受托人，唔係你話交一蚊租就一蚊租<img src=\"/assets/f