嘅借貸上限 &amp; MPF管理局亦建議未來港人MPF 投資組合可以有更大比例嘅房託投資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oedp3Te.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foedp3Te.png&h=00b16c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而今日新鮮出爐有晒招股書嘅順豐房託, 正正中晒我上篇所講嘅注意事項<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n======================================================<br />\nPoint 1, 負債問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tA4jrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tA4jrJ.png&h=59599298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於最右手邊, 2020年09月30日<br />\n總資產 HKD$60.95億 物業值 $60.46億<br />\n計息負債總額: 借貸 + 關連方貸款 = HKD $29.77億<br />\n借貸額佔總資產值 48.8%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zf7Vq6N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzf7Vq6N.png&h=36609f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而跟據房託守則, 借上限係50%<br />\n好明顯已經貼近借貸上限, 若果他日需要有新收購(增長)<br />\n你地覺得供股機會大唔大? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"基本上就係cap 水，派垃圾，買都on99"},{"pid":"07c28d2ed1ee13e4bc729c7439ca8369bc3a3957","tid":2402053,"uid":86449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8cc04b1a34339a30477b4bad255b1aa83e4ae280","tid":2402053,"uid":64345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e51d3971261893853dade393870ed97a9ab3845","tid":2402053,"uid":246729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7107d659d5b93485a82a1477646459452d411324","tid":2402053,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"各大房托（778 435 808 ）會唔會開始有收購動作？<br />\n放寬左條例+低息環境 +資產負債比例低 <br />\n今年似係一個適合reits去併購物業既時機"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"希望會<br />\n講size， 相對有能力收購嘅係 2778 &amp; 778<br />\n(0823 更加唔洗講)<br />\n<br />\n2778 , 有800億物業<br />\n778 , 有400億物業<br />\n印像中大約20% 借貸比率<br />\n有極大空間做新收購<br />\n奈何依兩間野 講左幾年都無做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年covid 海外大平賣, 2778又話做唔到 盡職審查 (20